{"tid":2322653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國內政部更新左BNO LOTR持有人的僱主指引","createTime":"2020-12-12T12:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T19:28:10.000Z","uid":28114,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"64130fb97d6d61511f516e3a807cd07d42ec0821","tid":2322653,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:59:43.000Z","msg":"Guidance<br />\nEmploying BN(O) citizens in the UK<br />\nInformation for employers on employing British National (Overseas) (BN(O)) citizens and their family members in the UK<br />\n<br />\nChecking a BN(O) citizen job applicant&rsquo;s right to work<br />\n<br />\nBN(O) citizens and their dependants granted Leave Outside the Rules at the border have the right to work in the UK. <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">BN(O) citizens can use a stamp in their passport as proof of their right to work </span>&ndash; this is confirmed in list B, group 1 of the code of practice on preventing illegal working. The stamp restricts their access to public funds but does not restrict their ability to work.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">You won&rsquo;t have to pay a penalty if you employ someone with this stamp in their passport </span>and you&rsquo;ve checked this allows them to work in the UK.<br />\n<br />\nBN(O) visa route<br />\nApplications for the BN(O) visa open from 31 January 2021. Applicants and their dependants under this route will also have the right to work. See more information about the BN(O) visa.<br />\n<br />\nFurther information about BN(O)s&rsquo; right to work will be published in 2021.<br />\n<br />\nPublished 11 December 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/employing-bno-citizens-in-the-uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Femploying-bno-citizens-in-the-uk&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=245b8f5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/employing-bno-citizens-in-the-uk</a>"},{"pid":"fc9d6008d4bd77425431d98e379f32c94cd5847f","tid":2322653,"uid":176935,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"thanks for clarifying"},{"pid":"fb664c339d0ae93243395596328118bb00907e41","tid":2322653,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:02:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b565c7667e1e544920006e10d885f473051535c","tid":2322653,"uid":282404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e25aec5e12a17b3a73ecf66bbf7632d3b69750f","tid":2322653,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a595591f4048c8056b70903faaa0c2325ebd26a","tid":2322653,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"藍屍港豬將會全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88faefe64a1eafd3438b2abd7ba4808ae724b382","tid":2322653,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:31:20.000Z","msg":"終於<br />\n<br />\n見到有好多人去到uk都話俾人拒絕tolr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0149df7c940e22f45d05f8ce23fbd007763d55","tid":2322653,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e46d971a897fda5ef1c6186c465b7d6401d2a54","tid":2322653,"uid":152476,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"間接證明唔少人過左去而且積極搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ada5fd6c44ddfb79b5a90a8ca8d6575fbcf7dc1","tid":2322